 and Tailwind to improve load times by 400% and user retention by 35%.\",\"project2_category\":\"E-Commerce App\",\"project2_title\":\"Premium Retail Experience\",\"project2_desc\":\"Native-feeling headless commerce application using React Native and Shopify Storefront API. Increased mobile conversion rates by over 120%.\"}}],[\"$\",\"$L16\",null,{\"dict\":{\"title\":\"How We Build\",\"subtitle\":\"An uncompromising approach to engineering.\",\"steps\":[{\"title\":\"Architecture Discovery\",\"desc\":\"We map out the precise technical requirements, data models, and infrastructure needs.\"},{\"title\":\"System Design\",\"desc\":\"Creating scalable database schemas and high-fidelity wireframes that convert.\"},{\"title\":\"Engineering Sprints\",\"desc\":\"Rapid, agile development using Next.js and robust cloud architectures.\"},{\"title\":\"Deployment & Scale\",\"desc\":\"Zero-downtime deployment, QA, and continuous performance optimization.\"}]}}],[\"$\",\"$L17\",null,{\"dict\":{\"hero\":\"$5:props:children:0:props:dict\",\"ticker\":{\"trusted\":\"Powered by industry-leading technologies\"},\"services\":{\"title\":\"Our Expertise\",\"web_dev\":{\"title\":\"Web Development\",\"desc\":\"Custom, high-performance web-scrolling experiences.\"},\"brand_web\":{\"title\":\"Personal Brand Web\",\"desc\":\"From Instagram to Web: A premium landing page for your brand.\"},\"meta_ads\":{\"title\":\"Meta Ads Audit\",\"desc\":\"Deep analysis and optimization of your advertising campaigns.\"},\"seo_audit\":{\"title\":\"SEO Audit\",\"desc\":\"Technical and content audit to dominate search results.\"},\"automations\":{\"title\":\"N8N Automations\",\"desc\":\"Save hundreds of hours with custom workflow automations.\"},\"pm\":{\"title\":\"Project Management\",\"desc\":\"Independent consulting and project leadership.\"}},\"work\":\"$5:props:children:2:props:dict\",\"process\":{\"title\":\"How We Work\",\"subtitle\":\"We don't just write code; we engineer solutions designed to scale from day one.\",\"step1\":\"Discovery & Strategy\",\"step1_desc\":\"We analyze your business needs and craft a tailored technical plan.\",\"arch_title\":\"Architecture & Design\",\"arch_desc\":\"We design scalable system architectures and beautiful UI/UX that align with your business goals.\",\"step2\":\"Development & Delivery\",\"step2_desc\":\"Agile building, rigorous testing, and a flawless launch.\",\"step3\":\"Growth & Maintenance\",\"step3_desc\":\"We ensure your product scales efficiently.\"},\"pricing\":{\"title\":\"Transparent SaaS Pricing\",\"setup\":\"Setup\",\"mo\":\"/mo\",\"one_time\":\"One-time\",\"retainer\":\"Retainer (mo)\",\"features\":\"Includes hosting, updates, and priority support.\"},\"testimonials\":{\"text1\":\"Arasue Forge transformed our entire digital infrastructure. Their architecture allowed us to scale from 10k to 500k monthly active users without a single hiccup.\",\"author1\":\"Sarah Jenkins\",\"role1\":\"CTO, Vertex Analytics\",\"text2\":\"The sheer speed and quality of their React development is unmatched. They don't just build apps, they build products that people love to use.\",\"author2\":\"David Chen\",\"role2\":\"Founder, Elevate\"},\"cta\":{\"title\":\"Ready to build?\",\"subtitle\":\"Stop compromising on your engineering quality. Partner with us and scale your digital products today.\",\"note\":\"Reply within 24 hours. No obligations.\"},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"Frequently Asked Questions\",\"q1\":\"Do you offer custom development outside these plans?\",\"a1\":\"Yes, we handle enterprise-grade custom applications. Contact us for a custom quote.\",\"q2\":\"What technologies do you use?\",\"a2\":\"We specialize in the React ecosystem (Next.js), Node.js, and cloud-native architectures.\",\"q3\":\"How does the SaaS web model work?\",\"a3\":\"Instead of a massive upfront cost, you pay a small setup fee and a monthly subscription that covers hosting, maintenance, and minor updates forever.\"},\"services_page\":{\"title\":\"Engineered for Do